{"tid":2487987,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"女咖啡師被控旺角警署外暴動及縱火罪成 判監4年半","createTime":"2021-04-14T02:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T02:45:43.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad72343809d95f977c49598943c226bc93c27a0","tid":2487987,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:34:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15009\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15009&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11PE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=916bad08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15009</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第廿八庭 <br />\n#姚勳智法官 #判刑<br />\n👤蕭(26) #0922旺角<br />\n🛑已還押20天🛑<br />\n<br />\n控罪1及2：縱火 #縱火罪<br />\n被告被控於2019年9月22日，在旺角太子道西及彌敦道交界，兩度用火摧毁或損壞屬於他人的財產。<br />\n<br />\n控罪3：暴動 #暴動罪<br />\n被告被控於同日同地參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n(*)控罪4，即「在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器」，已被法庭裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n📌法庭就本案的裁決理由及本案的審訊內容索引：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14607&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11PE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=1d67f15a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14607</a><br />\n==============<br />\n控方代表：#李穎賢署理高級檢控官<br />\n辯方代表：#關恆芬大律師<br />\n==============<br />\n📌以下是判刑結果：<br />\n<br />\n控罪1以4年即時監禁作為量刑起點<br />\n控罪2以4年即時監禁作為量刑起點<br />\n控罪3以4年6個月即時監禁作為量刑起點<br />\n<br />\n🛑最後，法庭就3項控罪合共判處被告人4年6個月即時監禁，同期執行...🛑<br />\n<br />\n其他內容會在今天內以另文補上。"},{"pid":"cc80605b1958ca98f7b73b4f5aaa45be19fdd4df","tid":2487987,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eca24b562e63274ea30c135530eb85ad77a9e6f","tid":2487987,"uid":15697,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"ci